                          search + mutex lock

  Memory overhead         64 shard structures,      Negligible
                          each with mutex and
                          unordered_map buckets

  Per-operation locking   Per-shard mutex           None

  Handle validation       Graceful nullptr on       Undefined behavior on
                          invalid lookup            stale pointer

